  "notes": "Southwest entrance to the Whirl Islands complex. The SW cave is the most interconnected entrance cave: it connects to the NW cave via a lower passage, has two staircases to B1F, AND has a direct passage to B2F — which is the only way to reach the Lugia Chamber short of going through the full B1F. It also has an actual surfable water pool (Tentacool/Horsea/Tentacruel at 4% rate) unlike the NW entrance. Contains one Ultra Ball at (15,2). Width 10 blocks / 20 tiles, height 9 blocks / 18 tiles. Source: maps/WhirlIslandSW.asm, constants/map_constants.asm line 133, data/maps/maps.asm line 146, data/wild/johto_grass.asm lines 901-927, data/wild/johto_water.asm lines 75-80."
